60.1	A_Scanner_Darkly_(film)	A Scanner Darkly (film)	A Scanner Darkly is a 2006 science fiction thriller directed by Richard Linklater based on the novel of the same name by Philip K. Dick. The film tells the story of identity and deception in a near-future dystopia constantly under intrusive high-technology police surveillance in the midst of a drug addiction epidemic. The movie was filmed digitally and then animated using interpolated rotoscope over the original footage, giving it its distinctive look.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/7/75/A_Scanner_Darkly_Poster.jpg/215px-A_Scanner_Darkly_Poster.jpg
